      "text": "Quiz nights return to Blue Turtle - Tuesday 7th November Tuesday, 24 October 2017 \nYou know it's nearing the end of the tourist season when this ever popular expat evening entertainment kicks in. \nQuiz nights return to the Blue Turtle Cafe Bar on Tuesday 7th November , starting at 20.00. \nThe quiz takes place most Tuesdays out of season, but may take the occasional break - check before you go. It would be true to say that some people take the quiz more seriously than others, (look for the furrowed brows), but at the end of the day, it is a fun event, and there is always a good atmosphere. \nEveryone is welcome. And if you fancy setting a quiz one week, let the organisers know, as they are always looking for guest quiz-masters. \nP.S. The owner of Blue Turtle, Barƒ±≈ü is returning to his home town of Izmir and a new owner is taking over. There is a farewell/handover party organised for Saturday 28th October, starting at 19.30. Good luck to both Barƒ±≈ü and to the new owners.",
