      "title": "Novartis delivered growth on top and bottom line in all divisions in Q3",
      "country": "GB",
      "crawl_date": "2017-10-24T07:30:47Z",
      "url": "https://www.bioportfolio.com/news/article/3388348/Novartis-delivered-growth-on-top-and-bottom-line-in-all-divisions-in.html",
